OL,6,FThe defendant denies two counts of
OL,7,Fmisconduct in a public office, one by
OL,8,Fhaving a relationship with Saunderson
OL,9,Fand the second by failing to disclose
OL,10,Fcounty court judgments about personal
OL,11,Fdebts.
OL,13,FShe also denies one count of
OL,14,Fpossessing criminal property, the
OL,15,FMercedes car, from Saunderson.
