OL,3,C'Hands-on' Prison Governor denies
OL,4,Cwrongdoing with convict
OL,6,FWhile working at HMP Liverpool in
OL,7,FMarch 2018, she told the jury she was
OL,8,Fcalled to a meeting with the main
OL,9,Fgovernor Robert Durgan, after the
OL,10,FPrison Service found out she had three
OL,11,FCounty Court Judgment's (CCJ) against
OL,12,Fher, which is against the rules for
OL,13,Fstaff as it may make them vulnerable
OL,14,Fto financial inducements.
OL,16,FPegg said she did not realise that not
OL,17,Fdeclaring or having a CCJ was breaking
OL,18,Fthe rules.
