OL,6,FShe said: "I was mortified, I was
OL,7,Fembarrassed, I started crying. But he
OL,8,Fwas really supportive and kind."
OL,10,FAndrew Alty, defending, asked if Mr
OL,11,FDurgan told her she should have
OL,12,Freported her CCJ's and this amounted
OL,13,Fto misconduct in a public office.
OL,15,FPegg replied: "No. He said they were
OL,16,Fnow 'known'. Declared. And there was
OL,17,Fno further disciplinary action to
OL,18,Ftake. He just gave me advice."
