OL,6,FThe defendant said staff at HMP
OL,7,FLiverpool were also aware she had had
OL,8,Fa breast enhancement procedure, and
OL,9,Fwas put on restricted duties for a
OL,10,Ftime to recover.
OL,12,FPegg said when she moved to HMP
OL,13,FKirkham in April 2018 as a governor,
OL,14,Fwhere Saunderson was coming to the end
OL,15,Fof a 10-year sentence for drugs
OL,16,Foffences, there were "cultural issues".
OL,18,FPegg said her "style" was always to
OL,19,Fhave and "open-door policy" and lots
OL,20,Fof contact with prisoners in the jail.
