OL,6,F"I have always been a hands-on person,
OL,7,Fhands-on manager, I like contact with
OL,8,Fpeople," she said.
OL,10,F"They really seemed to appreciate it,
OL,11,Fthey really appreciated someone
OL,12,Fwilling to listen to them. They felt
OL,13,Fthey had been ignored by other staff."
OL,15,FPegg admitted that she had signed off
OL,16,Fon Release on Temporary Licence (ROTL)
OL,17,Fform, for Saunderson in October 2018,
OL,18,Fwhich should only have been signed off
OL,19,Fby another official, the acting duty
OL,20,Fgovernor.
