OL,6,FEarlier the trial heard, Saunderson
OL,7,Fwas released from prison in May 2019,
OL,8,Fand in early 2020 was using an
OL,9,FEncrochat encrypted mobile phone, used
OL,10,Fby serious, organised criminals to
OL,11,Fsend messages and secretly
OL,12,Fcommunicate, the court heard.
OL,14,FWhen the system was cracked by law
OL,15,Fenforcement agencies it showed
OL,16,FSaunderson went by the handle or
OL,17,Fpseudonym of Jesse Pinkman and was
OL,18,Finvolved in massive drug trafficking.
OL,19,FHe has since been convicted for those
OL,20,Foffences.
